# Local Vite / workerd (detached)

URL: `http://localhost:5173/` (prefer `localhost`). Detached manager so Vite
outlives agent shell reaping. Foreground `npm run dev` is for humans.

| Command | Use |
|---|---|
| `npm run dev:status` | Health check first |
| `npm run dev:start` | Bring up if down |
| `npm run dev:stop` | Stop managed process |
| `npm run dev:restart` | Only if down, user asks, or env/bindings/Vite/deps changed |
| `npm run dev:logs` | Read `.dev-server.log` |

Do **not** restart for routine source edits (HMR). Prefer these scripts over
raw `npm run dev` / `pkill`. PID/log: `.dev-server.pid` / `.dev-server.log`
(gitignored). Catalog: `scripts/README.md` → `scripts/dev-server.sh`.
`dev:start`/`dev:restart` may need unsandboxed/`all` permissions (sandbox can
fail with `uv_interface_addresses`).
